This endpoint allows the user to register a new campaign.

### Request Body

- `name` (string, required): The name of the campaign.

- `description` (string): A brief description of the campaign.

- `startDate` (string, required): The start date of the campaign in the format DD/MM/YYYY.

- `endDate` (string, required): The end date of the campaign in the format DD/MM/YYYY.


